    <h1>Supply-Side Platform (SSP)</h1>
    <p class="description">Ad technology used by publishers to sell their advertising inventory programmatically across multiple exchanges and demand platforms simultaneously. SSPs run <strong>real-time bidding auctions</strong> for each available impression, maximising publisher revenue through competitive buyer access.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
